*Jedan* dan sam proveo u planini. (I spent one day in the mountains.)
On je *jedan* od najboljih učenika u školi. (He is one of the best students in the school.)
Došla je s *jednom* knjigom u rukama. (She came with one book in her hands.)
Dala mi je *jedan* savjet. (She gave me one advice.)
*Jedno* od najboljih mesta za odmor je obala. (One of the best places for vacation is the coast.)